=09Tesla=E2=80=99s board is going to be like =E2=80=9Csure yes of course, w=
hatever you want.=E2=80=9D=09Then Tesla will ask shareholders to vote to ap=
prove the relocation, as Musk  has already said it will do.=09Some sharehol=
