WRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTI0MDIxMiZ1dG1fY2Ft=
cGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cD14e13500" itemprop=3D"Story=
Link" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; te=
xt-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-col=
or: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Tesla is=
 different</a>. It does make sense that Musk would want <a href=3D"https://=
link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34321970.285393/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb=
